@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

node "Student Laptop" as StudentDevice
cloud "Public Wi-Fi\nUntrusted Network" as Wifi
node "EduSecure Server" as Server {
  artifact "Vue Frontend"
  artifact "Spring Boot API"
}
database "PostgreSQL\nplaintext credentials / weak storage" as Db

StudentDevice --> Wifi : HTTP
Wifi --> Server : HTTP credentials, tokens, grades, submissions
Server --> Db : plaintext / weakly protected sensitive records

note right of Wifi
Traffic can be intercepted or modified.
MITM and eavesdropping risk are high.
end note

note right of Db
Sensitive records are vulnerable if the database is exposed.
end note
@enduml

